{
  "stem": "10.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "elapsed_s": 46.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Leave all young people, release who are able to work for one day only, see?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we released them at night, and during the day they went to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When the doctor came, made the selections, they were safe, because they didn't take part in the selection, see?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So after night, the evening when they came back from work, we admitted them again to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saved hundreds of people this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the doctor said after two weeks, regardless, when he didn't recuperate, selection out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What we did-- some young people, they were already two weeks and they didn't recuperate yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were due to go out to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We changed the records.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The wrong name-- another name, another number, or we transferred him in another room, you know, to be a little longer in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was our work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our doctors?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From time to time they got medicine like I got, you see, when I was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the factory our engineers, they built x-ray machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they built the first electric shock machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was actually discovered in the camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in our hospital the German doctors made experiments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They brought, from the woman camp, about 12 to 15 young girls, young women, mentally already sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They brought them once a week, and they experimented in our hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I once took part in it, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The shock machine, an instrument, big like an x-ray machine, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And attached, naturally, different wires.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They attached them to the head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they starting giving shocks, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a few shocks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to tell you, some died right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other ones were still alive, but I don't know if anyone recuperated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this was the first actual experiments with electric shocks, which actually is being done now too, till now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was in our hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All other experiments, they were done in the main camp in Auschwitz, not by us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The experiments Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mengele did on women, the sexual experiments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He, for instance, gave shots into eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He tried to change the color of the eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He wanted them all to make blue eyes like the Germans, the Aryan race.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, till now, there's an organization of the twins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He experiment on the twins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm very active on this organization too, about Mengele.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had many conferences after the war, in United States and in Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we still are after Mengele.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We don't think he's dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He might have died, maybe yesterday, or two months ago, who knows, maybe last year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that time, when it came to the point to say he's dead, he was not dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there is a dentist, a woman dentist in Brazil, who has his x-rays from his teeth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we compared the teeth of the body with these x-rays, and they did not compare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't identify.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we think it's not his body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, even less than a month, somebody called me, a woman from Salt Lake City.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a habit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She looks after Mengele-- how he died, where he was, if he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she thinks this is the body of his brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we don't know, but this is separate, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In Auschwitz this went on-- yes, but I was there in the beginning a week, and I returned from the Sunday, from the football game, from the soccer game.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My block eldest, my camp eldest isn't there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, I laid down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the morning he's not there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had to give the report to the SS men, the roll call.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he comes to the camp, and I give him the report, saw so many people-- one is missing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They knew already that one is missing because [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] the fence was cut, and he escaped.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he could escape because this spot of the camp, on Sunday when all the people in the camp not going out to work, this was not occupied.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Only the fence was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He did say escape on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He went through and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They never caught him, and we never knew what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we think he made it to the Poles, in the mountains, but he was killed right away because he didn't speak Polish, only German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They considered him as a spy and they killed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rudy Kahn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a German-Jew and half-Jew, and no trace about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a while when the SS men reported that they found the missing one-- I mean, he is from the re-educational camp, the kapo, the block eldest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was called to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
